title: Guide7 Changelog Build 20:
message:
Guide7 Changelog Build 20:

- Guide7 is now ready for Android 8.0 Oreo
- Fixed login issues (ZPA changed to another certificate)
- More pretty login dialog
- Fixed link clicking issues in the notice board
- Improved notice board scrolling performance for weaker devices
- Links in appointments are now clickable
- Improved appointment parsing
- Improved appointment view scrolling performance
- Greatly increased schedule loading performance

title: - Filterable Appointments
message:
- Filterable Appointments
- Appointment Notifications
- Several small bugfixes

title: - Fixed bug where the static notification was still shown despite the event has been cancelled
message:
- Fixed bug where the static notification was still shown despite the event has been cancelled
- Canteen Menu is working again

message:

- Fixed static notification for next event.

message:
